data.description: Stunning Four bedroom home located in Fenton Estates in Cary! Home gets tons of natural light and has a fresh coat of neutral grey paint to show it all off. Brand new quartz countertops in fully tiled and open kitchen with loads of counterspace and cabinets. Separate formal dining room with trey ceiling. Wet bar located in family room can be open or closed off. Nice sized bedrooms and the master has its own sitting area. The large fenced in backyard boasts both a deck and patio perfect for that morning cup of coffee or glass of wine at sunset. Roof and HVAC are both just a few years old and the masonite siding has been replaced with hardiplank and freshly painted. Move in ready!
